{"tid":1163281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(引渡惡法) 黃洋達: 中共將大耍金錢力撐香港, 但香港人不要被騙","createTime":"2019-05-20T11:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T03:17:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":187,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"c788b043fe47f1634253133514db9c428caeafc9","tid":1163281,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:03:32.000Z","msg":"黃洋達:<br />\n<br />\n- 中美冷戰原本應該非常有利香港, 除非有「自己人」想整死香港.<br />\n- 《逃犯條例》修訂會整死香港, 香港係國際上既特殊位置會無哂, 美國關係法會取消.<br />\n- 中共唔介意借摧殘自己領土既經濟, 去保住自己既權力.<br />\n- 美國強烈反對《逃犯條例》修訂, 但中共硬推下, &nbsp;《逃犯條例》修訂最後都極可能會通過. &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>- &nbsp;但中共非常愛面子. 我佔計,&nbsp; &nbsp;《逃犯條例》修訂通過後, 中共將大耍金錢力撐香港兩年, 證明香港無左國際支持一樣掂. &nbsp; 但香港人不要被騙.<br />\n- 《逃犯條例》修訂通過後, 香港基本上已經係「腦死亡」. &nbsp;在中共力撐香港兩年間所做成既表面風光, 都只係迴光返照. &nbsp;之後香港就會完全死亡.</strong><br />\n<br />\n- 在中共死撐香港期間, 中共同香港政府亦會加快搾乾香港資源去益大灣區. &nbsp; 大灣區最後未必會成功, 但香港就死硬.<br />\n<br />\n- 中國最後可能會步入內戰, 但不會在2020年發生.<br />\n- 色魔龍緯汶被捕, 一定要歸功於連登仔.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1366\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F85%2F1366&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGUx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=60662b4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/85/1366</a>"},{"pid":"bd5e3c56886db60b871c84e1f1ef51b3ebe04d6e","tid":1163281,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ebd4f0b66c75b2bc44990706095bc4cf11ab64","tid":1163281,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:14:12.000Z","msg":"推推。  香港人不要被騙"},{"pid":"6d23961f462cc59d04c8e1e58e86f9f2fe67e58c","tid":1163281,"uid":163350,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:16:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db1201848c44337b6075dc25dffba08038d3e213","tid":1163281,"uid":93000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c2a49012ea812e32acb1fe163293613d9767a7","tid":1163281,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7d1b4d7447b10fc6f142b09035b19f0d52d3b6","tid":1163281,"uid":191926,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"黃洋達就快可以反cap仇思達"},{"pid":"8836d788f4126e0159cc70bb11749528ea6dc0ca","tid":1163281,"uid":41116,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"鳩達心諗<br />\n好在我上次醒去台灣燒支那旗"},{"pid":"04192bb76f4b8604d1ba1a261aeebd5511b12dbc","tid":1163281,"uid":61280,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:20:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次鳩達好似又有point</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今朝食啱藥頂啦！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252884e5c766495e8bfbee3d7c3911e982eef581","tid":1163281,"uid":13663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"1. 全面關稅下 中國出口減外匯減 印錢機已慶武功<br />\n2. 香港爆左關係法 上市發債cap能力大減<br />\n3. 那有錢 你老母"},{"pid":"55294af0c986f762f7f6abe8f760a3bff44234df","tid":1163281,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:22:34.000Z","msg":"波叔都講到明啦, 大家要迎難而上<br />\n食樹皮都要頂住呀到時 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70b6b6f7360d8fac47ac461eaeb679d000181c6","tid":1163281,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T11:23:35.000Z","msg":"今次講得幾中肯"},{"pid":"247b6f0